    <item>
      <title>如何统一计算自己的收益率</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/2023/how-to-calculate-your-own-rate-of-return-in-a-unified-manner/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
